      "text": "<p>Vasa <code>blue-box</code> klasa treba da postavi <code>margin</code> na <code>20px</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "const blueBox = document.querySelector('.blue-box');\nconst marginTop = window.getComputedStyle(blueBox)['margin-top'];\nassert.strictEqual(marginTop, '20px');"
